title: Empire Wreckers Actual Play Podcast - Campaign Premiere

media:group.media:title: Empire Wreckers Actual Play Podcast - Campaign Premiere
media:group.media:description:
Before our youtube channel, Empire Wreckers started out as an actual play podcast using the Fantasy Flight Games Star Wars RPG system.

For anyone who might be interested, we've uploaded the first episode of our new campaign to youtube. If you're interested in checking out the rest of our adventures, you can find Empire Wreckers on most audio streaming services, or find the episodes directly at:

https://www.buzzsprout.com/141856/
